                <p><lb n="1"/><gap reason="lost"/> <supplied reason="lost">sava</supplied><unclear>sa</unclear>tutamasa <space/> naravasabhasaṁmasaṁbudhādicasa <g type="punctuation" ref="sym:ddanda"/> Upāsakasa <space/> nārasalasa <space/> vāniyasa <space/> nāgatisasa <space/> gharaṇiya <space/> nākhāya <space/> sahā Apano <space/> putehi <space/> heraṁṇik<unclear>e</unclear>na <space/> budhinā <space/> mūlena <gap reason="lost"/></p>
            </div>
